							  Some text in the modal. Some text in the modal. Some text in the modal.Some text in the modal.Some text in the modal.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="modal-footer">
				<button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">fermer</button>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</div>{% endblock %}
